<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="insult-n">insult <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'sʌlt/    美 /ɪn'sʌlt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>侮辱；辱骂；冒犯：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their offer was so low I took it as an insult. 
他们的出价太低，我认为是一种侮辱。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>insulting /ɪn'sʌltɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>